ana).', 'media_src': 'https://bi.im-g.pl/im/72/c0/16/z23858802V,Michal-Kwiatkowski.jpg', 'media_desc': 'Michał Kwiatkowski', 'media_type': 'image', 'comments': []}, 'timestamp': 1559710906.714912}}